{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_07_end","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_07_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-7","storyName":"生灵火花","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"从战场逃离后，风笛的情绪终于爆发，她质问苇草小丘郡事件的真相，以及有关深池的一切。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_07_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_07","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["“校官”","菲舍尔","阿赫茉妮","特别行动队队长","维恩","陈","苇草","风笛","塔拉流民","莫兰"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g4_swamp_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","volume":"0.9","loop":"true","channel":"walksp","id":9},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":11},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"walksp","fadetime":"1","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"等一等，阿赫茉妮。","id":13,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"前方公路关卡的驻军数量有些异常。","id":14,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"您注意到了？我恰好还告诉过他们留意......这里也许会发生一些破坏公爵间关系的事件。","id":16,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_723_1#6$1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"......所以你必须赶在那些人离开特伦特郡辖区之前动手围捕，这样你留的后手才能够起效。","id":18,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"不算意外。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......威灵顿公爵手下，赤铁近卫队的长官，当然，这个身份很快就威胁不到您了。","id":22,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"不过，您至少很清楚，继续追击下去，事情会变成两位大公爵的领地争端。在当前维多利亚的局势下，恐怕没人想看到这样的冲突发生。","id":23,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哎呀，为什么你总是不给我留一些选择余地呢？","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"不过，现在这样也够了，我的任务也已经完成了。","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"你的失误造成了这样的恶果。作为身份已经暴露的间谍，你没有必要再如此尽职地虚张声势。","id":28,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"是吗？我可是真心希望，我们能共同为有朝一日的合作付出努力——","id":30,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_723_1#5$1","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"阿赫茉妮。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"你在台上说的话已经够多了。","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#3","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"咳......","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......","id":37,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"所有人，收队。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“校官”","text":"这原本就是一场败仗，先放过他们。","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_723_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":41},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","volume":"0.9","loop":"true","channel":"walksp1","id":42},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":43},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"walksp1","fadetime":"2","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":45},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#3","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":47},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","volume":"0.4","loop":"true","channel":"ahmnwalk","id":48},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":49},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"ahmnwalk","fadetime":"2","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":51},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"嘶......","id":53,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"特别行动队队长","text":"......我提醒过你，菲舍尔。矿石病发展到一定程度之后，这些止疼药就不管用了。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"特别行动队队长","text":"现在的情况，就是你长时间持续使用源石技艺的后果。","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"我当然知道。","id":58,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......","id":59,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"特别行动队队长","text":"......好吧，如果我话说得太重，我道歉。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"不，我只是在想......","id":63,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"尊敬的开斯特公爵竟然派来了一位“灰礼帽”。","id":65,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"而我甚至不知道......那位公爵的密使是什么时候取代了我的人。","id":66,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":67},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":68},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":69},{"type":"Character","id":70},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g4_swamp_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":71},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":72},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":74},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#5$1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"呼......哈......我们，我们是不是逃出来了？","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"嗯，后面看不到追兵了。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"先停下来检查一下受伤的情况吧，及时处理。","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我们......失去了几名伙伴。","id":81,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#7$1","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"在这里等等吧，烟雾里有人被冲散了，也许还躲在树林里。","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"之前你跟他们说好的前进方向是这边，如果他们还记得，应该会找过来。","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，我们只稍微停留一会儿。天就要亮了，我不会耽误你们的行程。","id":87,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"其他人也可以放下武器，暂时休息......","id":88,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":89},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......","id":91,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......风笛？","id":93,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":94},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.7","id":95},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i06","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"0.2","id":96},{"type":"background","id":97},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"200","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-100","yTo":"-100","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"0.3","block":"false","id":98},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.3","id":99},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":100},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.7","id":101},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"$distressed_loop","volume":"0.4","id":102,"musicid":1},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"“苇草”。","id":103,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"所以你就是小丘郡的那个术师。","id":104,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你就是那场火的操纵者。我认识你的法术，你让整条街道变成了灰烬。","id":105,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你让Outcast为救你而死。","id":106,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......你就是深池的“领袖”，是吗？","id":107,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":108,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":109},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"Text","text":"所有人全都在看着她，在等一个回答。","id":111},{"type":"Text","text":"这个问题，她从过去到现在听过许多次。每次听到的时候，她都需要拼命遏制自己摇头的欲望。","id":112},{"type":"Dialog","id":113},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"Character","id":115},{"type":"charslot","id":116},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":117},{"type":"delay","time":"-0.4","id":118},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i02","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":120},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":121},{"type":"Text","text":"可她想起了干草垛的触感和晚风的味道。","id":122},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i01","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"Text","text":"她想起帐篷前跃动的篝火，和枪尖上的火截然不同。","id":127},{"type":"dialog","id":128},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"image","id":130},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_coldforest","screenadapt":"showall","id":131},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":132},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_dim_closeeye","layer":"1","id":133},{"type":"bgeffect","id":134},{"type":"Text","text":"她想起远处还未完全消散的浓烟，那一声声呼喊仿佛仍有回声。","id":135},{"type":"dialog","id":136},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"background","id":138},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":139},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"这一次，她不再想摇头。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":140},{"type":"subtitle","id":141},{"type":"dialog","id":142},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"Dialog","id":144},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i06","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"1","x":"-30","y":"-30","id":145},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":146},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"-30","yFrom":"-30","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.85","duration":"20","block":"false","id":147},{"type":"Delay","time":"4","id":148},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":150},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我是。","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"在小丘郡的时候，我想以死永远摆脱我的身份，所以源石炮弹落下时我没有躲开。","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"罗德岛救起我之后，我试图为自己的命运扳回什么，所以我踏上这趟旅程，试图抚平一些深池的暴力留下的伤痕。","id":154},{"type":"multiline","name":"苇草","text":"但此刻，对于你的这个问题，我只会回答，","id":155},{"type":"multiline","name":"苇草","text":"我是。","id":156},{"type":"Dialog","id":157},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"Character","id":160},{"type":"image","id":161},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":162},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g4_swamp_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":163},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":164},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":166},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"那些死去的人......因深池而死的人。“塔拉人”。","id":168,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"深池......欺骗他们了，不是吗？","id":169,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......过去我会说，那些人的生命，不过是深池之火的燃料。","id":171,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"为了大局，为了全体塔拉人能起身反抗身上的不公，这把火必须烧得很旺很旺。","id":172,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但那些话......在我被Outcast救下，在我重新走过这些路之后，我没有办法再说出口。","id":174,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"实际上，总有一些死亡，原本是可以避免的。","id":175,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我不能说，所有的死难者，他们都是为深池的大业而牺牲的......塔拉人是一个又一个活着的，活生生的人。","id":176,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我记得深池犯的错......尤其是我亲手犯下的那些。我不会去掩盖这些丑陋的伤痕。","id":177,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"还有......“赤铁近卫队”。","id":179,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"今晚想带走你的深池士兵，是威灵顿公爵的人。","id":180,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你们......是公爵的私兵？","id":181,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不，深池的背后并没有......也不该有任何势力。","id":183,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"如果有，那就是......所有想要安宁的家乡，想在自己的土地上自由行走的塔拉人。","id":184,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"可是你很怕深池。","id":186,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"要是深池真的如你所说，是为了保护塔拉人而战，那你在害怕什么？","id":187,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":189,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我在怕......什么？","id":190,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你想象中的深池很好，可是实际上里面全都是暴徒、阴谋家、你控制不了的人。你甚至都被他们扔在了外面，不是吗？","id":192,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我不会否认，许多人在深池的火光里，看到的不是塔拉人的道路，只是自己的未来。","id":194,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我想......维多利亚人一砖一石地垒砌自己的家园时，也不会想起，自己在为维多利亚而付出。","id":195,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"只不过，维多利亚人已经有他们的家园和土地了，可以平静地建造、耕耘。塔拉人想要活着，却要流很多血。","id":196,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我不想看见任何人流血。是的，我很害怕，害怕流血，害怕死亡......所以我总想着躲起来。","id":197,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不去思考，不去感受，就像一个......影子。","id":199,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但是这样就可以了吗？为什么在我看不见的地方，血......还在流？","id":200,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"苇草......","id":202,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......风笛。你们之前总是问我，要带着这些塔拉人往哪里走。","id":204,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"现在我问你，深池的梦想是不能实现的吗？","id":206,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......","id":208,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Dialog","id":209},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":210},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":211},{"type":"Text","text":"风笛很少觉得失望。","id":212},{"type":"Text","text":"她想过自己的报告书永远交不到正确的人手里，也想过自己的战友们是在预谋已久的争端中无谓地牺牲。","id":213},{"type":"Text","text":"她想过自己再次面对深池的时候要如何瓦解他们的阴谋，从他们手中保护无辜的平民百姓。","id":214},{"type":"Text","text":"但现在，她看到了小丘郡事件背后只是公爵之间的彼此试探，也看到了苇草身后那几个从战火中走出来的塔拉人迷茫又惊惶的眼睛。","id":215},{"type":"Text","text":"她说不上来自己在对谁失望。","id":216},{"type":"Text","text":"她不知道自己还能从苇草口中得到什么答案，就如她同样回答不了苇草的问题。","id":217},{"type":"Dialog","id":218},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......该走了，陈。","id":221,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#6$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"嗯？","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"我的任务是调查深池的真相。现在，我听深池“领袖”亲口说清楚了。","id":225,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"还有，苇草干员听起来暂时不会跟着我们回罗德岛。","id":226,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":228,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"她还有自己的事要做，我们也有我们的。","id":230,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......好。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":233},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","volume":"0.7","loop":"true","channel":"walksp2","id":234},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1.5","id":235},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"walksp2","fadetime":"2","id":236},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":237},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_shallowsrun","volume":"1","id":238},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":239},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"风、风笛！","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......维恩？","id":243,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"这个......送给你。","id":245,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"收音机？","id":247,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"你们之后还要在荒野上赶路吧？拿着这个收音机，说不定能听到什么有用的消息......","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你不需要它了吗？","id":251,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我......哈哈，关于塔拉人的消息，不总是翻来覆去那几样吗？","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"风笛，我们真的很感谢你，感谢陈，感谢那个......罗德岛。谢谢你们的帐篷和这一路上的帮助。","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"还有......再见。","id":256,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......","id":258,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"再见，维恩。","id":260,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Dialog","id":261},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":262},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.3","id":263},{"type":"Text","text":"老旧的收音机在风笛手中发出一阵嗞嗞声。她下意识地放轻了手上的力道。","id":264},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"保重。","id":266,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Dialog","id":267},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":268},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":269},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"Character","id":271},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g3_swamp_d","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","screenadapt":"showall","id":272},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":273},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"$loneliness_loop","volume":"0.4","id":274,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":276},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......凯莉，费加尔，你和我。我们现在就剩下这八个人了。","id":278,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"人少一些，倒是容易跑路，哈哈......","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......","id":282,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......请帮我找一下，手提箱里还有没有干净的纱布。","id":284,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":285},{"type":"multiline","name":"维恩","text":"唉，好......","id":286},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_cardboard","volume":"0.8","id":287},{"type":"multiline","name":"维恩","text":"给。","id":288},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"现在我要把伤口附近的布料揭开，会很疼......","id":290,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":291},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":292},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.2","id":293},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-70","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":295},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.7","id":296},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":297},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":298},{"type":"shake","name":"left","power":"10","times":"100","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"嘶......","id":300,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"......欸，维恩，你没那么怕血了？","id":301,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"啊？是、是这么回事......见了这么多，怕也没办法呀。","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"唉，苇草......风笛真的就这么走啦？你们不是朋友吗？","id":304,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......也许，以后有一天还会是，但眼下不可能了。","id":306,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......唉，好吧。","id":308,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我就是觉得，虽然她们本来也要走，可是你和她们应该好好告别的。","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"所有人......都应该有一声道别的。","id":310,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":311},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":312},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#4$1","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"——欸，莫兰！","id":314,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":316,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":317},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":318},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":319},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","volume":"0.7","loop":"true","channel":"walksp3","id":320},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":321},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":322},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"walksp3","fadetime":"1","id":323},{"type":"Text","text":"他们看见莫兰借着黎明的微光，一瘸一拐地从远处走来。","id":324},{"type":"Text","text":"她的手里紧紧地攥着一把断掉的剑，还有一条沾满鲜血的头巾。","id":325},{"type":"Dialog","id":326},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"那是......塞尔蒙的？","id":328,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......莫兰，她最后......怎么了？","id":329,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","id":330},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"（沉默地摇头）","id":331,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......抱歉，你应该没能看见。","id":333,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":334},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":335},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":336},{"type":"BackgroundTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"0","yTo":"-70","duration":"10","block":"false","id":337},{"type":"Text","text":"远处的丛林间，战火燃烧过后的余烟还在缓缓地升向天空。","id":338},{"type":"Text","text":"和塞尔蒙一样，没有回来的人正躺在那片树林里。谁都没来得及看到，他们最后是什么样子。","id":339},{"type":"Text","text":"幸存者们沉默地注视着飘散的烟。","id":340},{"type":"Dialog","id":341},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":342},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......他们所有人，都只是......不知去向。","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"在石高原野，在小丘郡，在橡林郡......","id":344},{"type":"Dialog","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"Text","text":"她看过许多场大火。在不同的地方，有人谋划战争与灾祸，争夺权力与声名。","id":347},{"type":"Text","text":"她看着普通人在其中挣扎，又无缘无故地死去。","id":348},{"type":"Text","text":"她抬起手，德拉克的火焰生出一朵小小的花。","id":349},{"type":"Text","text":"握着火焰的感觉依然让她颤抖，让她的脏腑疼痛不已，但她却不再闭上眼睛。","id":350},{"type":"BackgroundTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"-70","xTo":"0","yTo":"70","duration":"20","block":"false","fadetime":"0.5","id":351},{"type":"Dialog","id":352},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":353},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"为所有......从这片泥泞的土地上爬起来的人们。","id":354},{"type":"Text","text":"小小的花朵飘摇落下，跌进沼泽，无声地枯败在烂泥之中。","id":355},{"type":"Dialog","id":356},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":359},{"type":"Character","id":360},{"type":"charslot","id":361},{"type":"Image","id":362}],"characters":["“校官”","菲舍尔","阿赫茉妮","特别行动队队长","维恩","陈","苇草","风笛","塔拉流民","莫兰"]}